{"tid":1631014,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武活動暫停，和理非活動進場","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:41:57.000Z","uid":25408,"like":66,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"eea92c0c185e6bfbedb908d2aaf9316e804b54dc","tid":1631014,"uid":25408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"人權法將近，我覺得我地應該暫停勇武活動，比啲時間文宣手足更新同埋發酵效果。<br />\n再者，人權法即將通過，最近有風向譴責放火同私鳥，因此呢個時候應該轉一下方向。<br />\n港共唔會因為你地裝修就怕，佢更怕係美國政權，比啲時間國際戰線做野<br />\n但叫停勇武絕唔代表休息，我地要繼續做下和理非活動，一來比前線手足休息入新裝，二來比啲時間大家討論方向取得共識。<br />\n<br />\n重申叫停勇武唔係想分化，覺得勇武無用，而係覺得和勇應該輪流上場，兩者不可忽略其一。詳細如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.18區修補/更新連儂牆</span></strong></span><br />\n文宣速度唔夠前線活動快，加上依家宣傳好似越來越少，有好多上左年紀既人跟唔上資訊，更新翻各區連儂牆可以宣傳同解釋翻近日活動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2.被裝修，裝飾既店鋪要痴牆紙</strong></span></span><br />\n眼見好多地鐵站同黑心店鋪被裝修後，手足無即時痴翻牆紙解釋原因，令附近居民甚至國際有留意香港既人好多時都唔知裝修既原因，為免令佢地誤會我地係唔係破壞，唔係無差別裝修，所以應該每次裝修後速痴牆紙解釋。<br />\n例如：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">黨鐵&gt;831，以及多次出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fdK9Koa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfdK9Koa.jpg&h=04fcb4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKWL19S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKWL19S.jpg&h=805b504d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">福建360&gt;8.5斬到手足傷殘</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qO99Kom.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqO99Kom.jpg&h=cceadc31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">美心集團&gt;太子女聯合國抹黑香港示威者，要求學校開除手足學藉</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScLAEWP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScLAEWP.jpg&h=a4c4c3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中資銀行&gt;中共逼害港人<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3.和理shop </strong></span></span><br />\n可以搞翻兩日全民去*傑出餐廳*食飯，涼冷氣，禁飛仔<br />\n例子：<br />\n元氣壽司&gt;飲茶，食酸薑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nw1sv3y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNw1sv3y.jpg&h=afa3a19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStarbucks&gt;坐低溫書做功課<br />\n各大酒樓&gt;輪流排隊拎飛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4.各大商場快閃唱歌叫口號</strong></span></span><br />\n手足可以帶不同面具,口罩一齊出席，又人數話比政府知就算有蒙面法我地都唔會驚佢，而且活動老少咸宜，全家大細都參加得，又有凝聚力又美觀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5.全民日日口罩</span></strong></span><br />\n唔洗講啦，依家又有伊波拉又肺炎<br />\n各位帶翻個口罩保護自己啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有無其他方法/意見？<br />\n歡迎手足一齊討論。"},{"pid":"b14ec35bb675ffe93f28ee1311a19abf74effd7f","tid":1631014,"uid":34404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:27:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0923942d078824ea6d65b25461d938c636132076","tid":1631014,"uid":78584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:30:15.000Z","msg":"到和理非出動既時候"},{"pid":"56b91540fc77b80bfc78888ed7b6527dc2b5a046","tid":1631014,"uid":292896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:30:35.000Z","msg":"和理非10日 只要人權法過到再勇武過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf8f09321773a68cff28f5a8f8e944585e75a5a","tid":1631014,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:30:55.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<b